                                {
                                    Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                    Operation: "EQUALS",
                                    Name: "royal_league_champion"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                    Operation: "EQUALS",
                                    Name: "no_defeated_port_challenger_2"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "muster_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Not this tide",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Battle Port. Fresh challengers daily - and today the roster posts two of us, because on this dock we fight as a crew. Two on two on the open water, house rules. The Company built this dock for spectacle, back when it built things for people. Care to test the water?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "One tide, one muster, all four hulls on the water at once - that is the whole trick of this dock. Crest sails at my shoulder, and Deckhand Maru takes your flank the moment you call it. Nothing of yours goes down on this floor. My rain is already falling."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Stern - the crew on shift",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
